 -- Robert James Clay <jame@rocasa.us>  Mon, 17 Dec 2018 10:41:11 -0500

ledgersmb-1.6 (1.6.6-2) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add '05_Makefile.patch' to facilitate running the upstream basic tests
    during a package build.
  * Changes to debian/control:
    + Derive Build-Depends-Indep from the Depends and Recommends stanzas.
    + Explicitly add 'libio-stringy-perl' to Depends and Build-Depends-Indep.
    + Explicitly add 'liblocale-codes-perl' to Depends and Build-Depends-Indep.
    + Add 'texlive-latex-recommended' & 'texlive-xetex' to the Build-Depends
      stanza.
    + Explicitly add 'libtest-trap-per' & 'libtest-exception-perl' to the
      Build-Depends-Indep stanza.
    + Replace 'libdbd-pg-perl' with 'libdbd-mock-perl' in Build-Depends-Indep
      stanza.
    + Explicitly add 'libdata-uuid-perl', 'libtext-markdown-perl',
      and 'libplack-middleware-reverseproxy-perl'  to the Depends stanza.
  * Remove the 'override_dh_auto_test' target from debian/rules to facilitate
    the running of basic upstream tests during a package build.

 -- Robert James Clay <jame@rocasa.us>  Sat, 10 Nov 2018 10:31:05 -0500

